1
00:00:20,960 --> 00:00:24,754
택시 창밖으로 번지는 불빛
The lights blurring outside the taxi window

2
00:00:26,498 --> 00:00:30,620
라디오에서 흘러나온 옛날 노래
An old song playing on the radio

3
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:37,299
이 시간엔 모든 게 느려져
At this hour, everything slows down

4
00:00:37,299 --> 00:00:41,527
너한테 갈까 말까 고민만 해
I just keep wondering if I should go to you

5
00:00:42,652 --> 00:00:46,625
편의점 앞 벤치에 앉아서
Sitting on the bench in front of the convenience store

6
00:00:47,195 --> 00:00:52,100
따뜻한 캔 하나 손에 쥐고
Holding a warm can in my hand

7
00:00:52,100 --> 00:00:57,317
네 연락을 기다리는 건 아닌데
It's not that I'm waiting for your call, but

8
00:00:57,509 --> 00:01:00,240
자꾸 화면을 확인하게 돼
I keep checking my screen

9
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:10,700
새벽 두 시 주파수가 맞는 밤
A 2 AM night when the frequency is right

10
00:01:10,700 --> 00:01:13,810
잡음 사이로 네 목소리가 들려
I hear your voice through the static

11
00:01:13,980 --> 00:01:20,180
이 도시가 잠들면 우리만 깨어서
When this city falls asleep, only we are awake

12
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:47,959
같은 하늘 아래 다른 곳에서
Under the same sky, in different places

13
00:01:48,784 --> 00:01:50,640
옥상에서 내려다본 골목길
The alleyway I look down on from the rooftop

14
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:53,159
가로등 하나가 깜빡이고 있어
A streetlamp is flickering

15
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:55,760
하고 싶은 말은 루프처럼 돌아
The words I want to say spin like a loop

16
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:58,841
입 밖으론 한마디도 못 꺼내
I can't utter a single word

17
00:01:58,959 --> 00:02:01,439
이어폰 한쪽만 끼고 걸어
I walk with only one earphone in

18
00:02:01,439 --> 00:02:04,120
네가 좋아하던 그 노래 틀어
I play that song you liked

19
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:06,620
발걸음이 리듬을 타는 밤
A night where my steps follow the rhythm

20
00:02:06,935 --> 00:02:08,659
혼자인데 혼자가 아닌 것 같아
I'm alone, but it doesn't feel like I'm alone

21
00:02:09,288 --> 00:02:13,000
새벽 두 시 주파수가 맞는 밤
A 2 AM night when the frequency is right

22
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:18,296
잡음 사이로 네 목소리가 들려
I hear your voice through the static

23
00:02:18,620 --> 00:02:24,906
이 도시가 잠들면 우리만 깨어서
When this city falls asleep, only we are awake

24
00:02:25,012 --> 00:02:31,979
같은 하늘 아래 다른 곳에서
Under the same sky, in different places

25
00:02:32,259 --> 00:02:34,240
전화할까 말까 세 번째 고민
It's the third time I'm wondering whether to call or not

26
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:39,564
나도 지금 네 번호 보고 있어
I'm looking at your number right now too

27
00:02:40,431 --> 00:02:45,240
새벽 두 시 주파수가 맞는 밤
A 2 AM night when the frequency is right

28
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:50,419
잡음 속에서 결국 너를 찾아
Finally, I find you through the static

29
00:02:50,419 --> 00:02:56,860
이 도시가 잠들어도 우리는 깨어서
Even if this city sleeps, we are awake

30
00:02:57,181 --> 00:03:00,379
같은 주파수로 이어져 있어
We are connected by the same frequency

